                     <interp inst="def1-320-18610408" type="given" value="JAMES"></interp>
                     <hi rend="largeCaps">JAMES TROTMAN</hi> (21)</persName>
                  <rs id="t18610408-320-offence-1" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18610408-320-offence-1" type="offenceCategory" value="royalOffences"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18610408-320-offence-1" type="offenceSubcategory" value="coiningOffences"></interp>, Feloniously uttering counterfeit coin.</rs>
